data.title: Vincent Price Art Museum Foundation proudly presents a 🪩 Summer Soiree: The Illuminators Gala at the Vincent Price Art Museum, on the...
data.meta_description:
vpam_arts on July 3, 2023: "Vincent Price Art Museum Foundation proudly presents a 🪩 Summer Soiree: The Illuminators Gala at the Vincent Price Art Museum, on the campus of @elachuskies, on 🗓️Saturday, July 29 at ☀️ 6:00 p.m. for our Dinner Program; followed by our 🌙 8:30 p.m. after dinner Summer Soiree– open to all!  VPAM’s Illuminator’s Gala is a the museum's premier fundraising celebration that includes special Honorees and guest speakers, dynamic performances by some of LA’s finest talent, plus stay tuned for an energizing art auction on @artsy, July 18-August 1, with proceeds benefiting VPAM! Get your Gala tickets today! Learn more at VPAM.org. 🔗 in bio. 

Our Gala opens at 6:00 p.m. with a Gala 🎨 art auction preview, 🍽️ dinner and 🎤 program honoring Arts Administrator and Cultural Producer, Betty Avila @bettyreznor, Charlie James Gallery @charliejamesgallery (accepted by Owner/Director, Charlie James + Curator and Gallery Manager, Ever Velasquez @ever.a.k.a.thegirlabouttown), Assemblymember Mike Fong @asmmikefong (49th District) and Giant Robot @giantrobot (accepted by Co-Founder, Eric Nakamura). The evening includes a curated dinner by ⭐️ #MichelinStar Chef Shin Thompson and the @NikuXla team, with a live 🎶 performance by The Gonzalez-Flores Trio, featuring Grammy Award Winning Musicians, Martha Gonzalez @marthartivista and Quetzal Flores @quetzalmusic with rising youth musician Sandino Gonzalez-Flores!

The #IlluminatorsGala program is followed by our after dinner #SummerSoiree at 8:30 p.m. with fun curated desserts by Boba X Ice Cream, 626 Hospitality Group @626hospitalitygroup, crafted @madremezcal and Condessa Gin cocktails by @chicasontherocks and music by 🎧 DJ Francesca Harding @thefrancescaharding (#KCRW 📻), with special 🎙️ live performances by Artists @Yozmit and @Polartropica for an unforgettable dance party! 📌Tip: Tickets to the dinner program includes free entry to the Soiree!

#VPAM #SummerSoiree #IlluminatorsGala #Museum #Art #Music #Dance  #Culture #MontereyPark #EastLA #EastLos".
